66
00:05:02,350 --> 00:05:05,389
Dun Dun, look! Your brother has learned how to walk.

67
00:05:05,389 --> 00:05:09,389
Jun Jun is a timid boy. You will get scared if you sleep outside alone.

68
00:05:09,389 --> 00:05:11,629
Sister! I don't like you anymore.

69
00:05:11,629 --> 00:05:15,100
Mom doesn't like you. Dad doesn't like you, either.

70
00:06:11,670 --> 00:06:16,579
Mom. She eats so much food! It's scary.

71
00:06:16,579 --> 00:06:18,819
