82
00:08:01,650 --> 00:08:04,369
Li Yun. Come in.

83
00:08:06,570 --> 00:08:10,019
Senior is having an affair with one of her visitors?

84
00:08:11,010 --> 00:08:13,590
But she's an experienced psychological counselor.

85
00:08:13,590 --> 00:08:15,380
How could she make this kind of mistake?

86
00:08:15,389 --> 00:08:17,060
Professor, is there some misunderstanding?

87
00:08:17,060 --> 00:08:20,559
We both know her husband Xu Wei. They were classmates back in university.

88
00:08:20,559 --> 00:08:22,450
They have been loving and respecting each other.

89
00:08:22,450 --> 00:08:23,750
I can't believe it.

90
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:26,440
Loving and respecting each other?

91
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:29,550
Do you know who reported it to the regulator?

92
00:08:29,550 --> 00:08:31,300
Who?

93
00:08:32,350 --> 00:08:33,640
Xu Wei.

94
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:37,860
He is my husband and my colleague.

95
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:41,700
He's also the co-founder of my psychological counseling agency.

96
00:08:41,700 --> 00:08:45,939
Then do you know why you are called to the hearing today?

97
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,910
Yes.

98
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:54,699
I assume my husband submitted a report to the relevant regulator.

99
00:08:55,860 --> 00:09:02,099
It's his statement on me having an intimate relationship with one of my visitors.

100
00:09:02,099 --> 00:09:05,769
Do you have something to defend yourself regarding this matter?

101
00:09:06,450 --> 00:09:08,110
No.

102
00:09:08,110 --> 00:09:10,840
Did she admit it herself?

103
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,030
Yes.

104
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:17,409
Originally I wanted to try my best to seize any opportunity so that she could defend herself.

105
00:09:17,409 --> 00:09:22,390
But I didn't expect that she would admit all the allegations against her in the hearing.

106
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:25,230
She said that she had seen Xu Wei's report.

107
00:09:25,230 --> 00:09:28,989
She even agreed with her husband to submit the report.

108
00:09:28,989 --> 00:09:31,060
In exchange,

109
00:09:31,060 --> 00:09:35,529
