00:13:20,749 --> 00:13:24,249
and broke through Li Yun's psychological defense mechanism.

168
00:14:22,930 --> 00:14:24,660
Jing Jing?

169
00:14:26,230 --> 00:14:27,980
Jing Jing?

170
00:14:29,540 --> 00:14:31,200
Jing Jing?

171
00:14:33,060 --> 00:14:34,610
Jing Jing.

172
00:14:35,780 --> 00:14:37,590
Dinner time.

