00:14:40,490 --> 00:14:43,860
Dr. Zhao called and asked about your situation.

174
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:46,939
I told him that you are much better now. How are you feeling now?

175
00:14:46,939 --> 00:14:49,000
Also, you almost run out of your medication, right?

176
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:52,180
Yes.

177
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:55,249
The medication prescribed by Dr. Zhao is working.

178
00:14:55,249 --> 00:15:00,459
Let's go see the doctor again some other time and ask him to give you some treatment.

179
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:06,649
Mom. I'm going to the movies with my friends tonight.

180
00:15:06,649 --> 00:15:09,230
