181
00:15:10,930 --> 00:15:14,300
This dress was the one I bought for you, right?

182
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:16,200
It's lovely.

183
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:20,670
Mom, actually…

184
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:22,250
Hello?

185
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:25,879
Hello? It's Le Le's mom.

186
00:15:25,879 --> 00:15:31,439
How many times have I told you that even though they've reached a high level playing the instruments,

187
00:15:31,439 --> 00:15:35,790
maybe they don't even know how they did it.

188
00:15:35,790 --> 00:15:39,009
So of course they wouldn't know how to teach their children.

189
00:15:39,009 --> 00:15:40,640
Am I right?

190
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:47,530
Give me a second.

191
00:15:47,530 --> 00:15:49,939
