192
00:15:49,939 --> 00:15:51,570
Yes.

193
00:15:54,780 --> 00:15:58,379
Yes. That's it.

194
00:15:58,379 --> 00:16:00,310
All right, now go.

195
00:16:00,310 --> 00:16:04,949
I am telling you, I found a very good music teacher for Jing Jing.

196
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,330
Over here!

197
00:16:51,330 --> 00:16:54,219
- Come on. Sit down! Dinner is on you.
- You came the latest today.

198
00:16:54,219 --> 00:16:56,060
- Yeah, I would give you a lecture had you come a bit later.
