199
00:16:56,060 --> 00:16:58,910
Let me tell you. The female drummer of our competitor for the contest next week is really awesome.

200
00:16:58,910 --> 00:17:01,340
- We need to watch out for her future.
- I know. I know that drummer.

201
00:17:01,340 --> 00:17:04,449
The drummer plays with particularly accurate beats but the tempos she inserts are so great.

202
00:17:04,449 --> 00:17:07,590
You know she is a good punk musician.

203
00:17:07,590 --> 00:17:10,260
So you mean it's a bit difficult for us to win the contest?

204
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:26,590
What's wrong, Jing Jing?

205
00:17:43,490 --> 00:17:46,329
What kind of weird workout is that?

206
00:17:46,329 --> 00:17:49,979
The highest honor in this courtyard. I shall allow you to hold my right foot.

207
00:17:51,740 --> 00:17:53,929
- What's going on?
- Jiahui taught me this.

208
00:17:53,929 --> 00:17:56,709
Raise my foot when I'm not walking around so it won't hurt so much.

209
00:17:56,709 --> 00:18:00,479
You are injured, too? Let me see. What is this plaster?

210
00:18:00,479 --> 00:18:02,520
