211
00:18:02,520 --> 00:18:06,310
My mom. She fell last night. So I stayed at our apartment last night and didn't come back here.

212
00:18:06,310 --> 00:18:08,870
How's she? Is she okay?

213
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:13,079
She refused to go to the hospital. I don't know what to do. How did you get this sprain? Let me see.

214
00:18:13,079 --> 00:18:16,870
It's nothing really. I sprained my ankle on my way to pick up my parcels.

215
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:20,379
Jiahui next door gave me acupuncture and it didn't hurt anymore.

216
00:18:20,379 --> 00:18:22,350
I didn't know he is so good.

217
00:18:22,350 --> 00:18:25,589
Speaking of which, isn't your mom also injured? You can ask him to give her some treatment, too.

218
00:18:25,589 --> 00:18:28,299
I can't trouble him to do that. Come on.

219
00:18:28,299 --> 00:18:31,429
No trouble at all. It's a piece of cake for him.

220
00:18:31,429 --> 00:18:33,090
- Forget it.
- Let's go.

221
00:18:33,090 --> 00:18:34,390
Why?

222
00:18:34,390 --> 00:18:37,270
