233
00:19:13,070 --> 00:19:14,170
This gentleman.

234
00:19:14,170 --> 00:19:17,319
You don't want to invite your neighbors to come in and sit down?

235
00:19:20,230 --> 00:19:21,230
Come on in.

236
00:19:21,230 --> 00:19:22,920
Thank you.

237
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:31,459
Jiahui. He Dun has a favor to ask you.

238
00:19:31,459 --> 00:19:36,839
Let me do the talking myself. So my mother fell and she doesn't feel so well.

239
00:19:36,839 --> 00:19:40,940
Lili said you are a good acupuncturist. So I was wondering if you can…

240
00:19:40,940 --> 00:19:42,280
Sure.

241
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,900
No hesitation at all.

242
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:46,660
You're really a good neighbor.

243
00:19:46,660 --> 00:19:48,560
Don't worry. I will pay you, of course.

244
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:52,799
What do you take me for? We're friends. This is the least I can do.

245
00:19:52,799 --> 00:19:54,329
Thank you.

246
00:19:54,329 --> 00:19:58,150
The biggest problem is that my mom doesn't want to go to the hospital no matter how I try to persuade her.

247
00:19:58,150 --> 00:19:59,640
I know what to do.

248
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:02,759
You will play the good cop and you just play the bad cop.

249
00:20:02,759 --> 00:20:07,719
You two can put up an act together to tell your mom that she needs to see a doctor and do more exercise.

250
00:20:07,719 --> 00:20:10,130
But you never played good cop bad cop with me to persuade her.

251
00:20:10,130 --> 00:20:13,210
The key is she won't listen to me.

252
00:20:13,210 --> 00:20:16,270
Besides, I'm not your boyfriend.

253
00:20:19,810 --> 00:20:21,820
Have some water. Just have your water.

254
00:20:21,820 --> 00:20:24,660
I feel like I am not needed here. I'll let you guys chat.

255
00:20:24,660 --> 00:20:26,759
The door is over there.

256
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:30,459
I feel like the third wheel here.

257
00:20:30,459 --> 00:20:33,779
Don't listen to her nonsense, she likes making jokes.

258
00:20:33,779 --> 00:20:35,760
She's a jokester.

259
00:20:37,520 --> 00:20:39,150
Don't be discouraged, Jiahui.

260
00:20:39,150 --> 00:20:41,830
He Dun specializes in psychology.

261
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:44,739
And you specialize in bruises, wounds, and sprained ankles.

262
00:20:44,739 --> 00:20:46,760
What do you special in then?

263
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:48,470
I am the soul of our courtyard.

264
00:20:48,470 --> 00:20:49,839
The social glue that holds this little group together.

265
00:20:49,839 --> 00:20:51,510
Without me maybe you two will never talk to or take a look at each other

266
00:20:51,510 --> 00:20:53,500
even if you brush past each other every day.

267
00:20:53,500 --> 00:20:55,040
That's not true.

268
00:20:56,520 --> 00:20:58,960
I will take the initiative to talk to Miss He.

269
00:21:01,950 --> 00:21:06,549
My mom may not be able to come here due to her physical inconvenience.

270
00:21:06,549 --> 00:21:08,820
Is it okay for you to go to her place with me later today?

271
00:21:08,820 --> 00:21:11,070
No problem.

272
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:13,560
Thanks.

273
00:21:13,560 --> 00:21:16,510
No, thanks, the cup is still full. Thanks.

274
00:21:17,470 --> 00:21:19,030
Enjoy the tea.

275
00:21:23,850 --> 00:21:25,460
Jing Jing.

276
00:21:25,460 --> 00:21:27,729
Have you gotten dressed yet?

277
00:21:27,729 --> 00:21:29,850
We need to go out for dinner with a friend of mine.

278
00:21:29,850 --> 00:21:32,470
Come on. Chop, chop.

279
00:21:36,660 --> 00:21:38,250
Jing Jing?

280
00:21:45,830 --> 00:21:46,970
Look at that.

281
00:21:46,970 --> 00:21:50,340
It's so dark in the room, why didn't you open the curtains?

282
00:21:56,940 --> 00:21:59,690
Jing Jing, are you okay?

283
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:04,029
Jing Jing! Jing Jing! Jing Jing!

284
00:22:05,760 --> 00:22:08,419
Jing Jing! Jing Jing, what's going on?

285
00:22:08,419 --> 00:22:10,110
I need to find help.

286
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:11,700
I need to find help.

287
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:24,060
She twisted her ankle and fell to the ground.

288
00:22:24,060 --> 00:22:27,590
The muscle contusion caused some swelling.

289
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:30,239
I will use massage techniques to adjust her muscles.

290
00:22:30,239 --> 00:22:32,030
Much better.

291
00:22:32,030 --> 00:22:34,070
Auntie, what do you think?

292
00:22:34,070 --> 00:22:35,830
Good. I feel better.

293
00:22:35,830 --> 00:22:40,529
Xiao Ye, I didn't expect you to be so good, I love it.

294
00:22:40,529 --> 00:22:42,529
Relax, then I will do an acupuncture

295
00:22:42,529 --> 00:22:46,529
at the three acupoints of Jiexi, Kunlun, and Qiuxu.

296
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:50,080
- Okay.
- You know what he's saying?

297
00:22:51,330 --> 00:22:52,950
Thank you.

298
00:22:52,950 --> 00:22:55,140
Can you give us some space?

299
00:22:56,660 --> 00:23:00,159
I am not used to being watched when I do acupuncture.

300
00:23:06,070 --> 00:23:09,761
I was kidding! I was thinking of doing a moxa-moxibustion on her foot.

301
00:23:09,761 --> 00:23:11,930
It will get better sooner.

302
00:23:11,930 --> 00:23:14,099
There are some moxa in my trunk.
(T/N: a form of heat therapy in which dried plant materials called "moxa" are burned on or very near the surface of the skin)

303
00:23:14,099 --> 00:23:15,740
Can you fetch some for me?

304
00:23:15,740 --> 00:23:18,589
No problem, give me your car key.

305
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,429
I'm going downstairs.

306
00:23:21,429 --> 00:23:23,180
Gentle.

307
00:23:24,090 --> 00:23:27,020
Mom is not afraid. I'm brave.

308
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:37,010
Auntie, I just used it as an excuse to send her away.

309
00:23:37,729 --> 00:23:41,630
You didn't sprain your ankle in an ordinary accident, right?

310
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:47,530
You feel dizzy often which caused the accident.

311
00:24:01,350 --> 00:24:04,669
[Giving your mom acupuncture isn't the only purpose! Ask her how she feels about the potential future son-in-law!]

312
00:24:04,670 --> 00:24:07,650
[Since you have no better things to do, why don't you go to our neighborhood committee to find a job?]

313
00:24:11,180 --> 00:24:13,850
[Moxa]

314
00:24:15,390 --> 00:24:19,370
[That's right! I can join the neighborhood committee and post a blind date ad for you in the group chat.]

315
00:24:19,370 --> 00:24:22,010
[Tang Lili, don't do anything stupid!]

316
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:27,880
Auntie, these are not prescription drugs.

317
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:31,010
Your dizziness is not necessarily caused by a high blood pressure.

318
00:24:31,010 --> 00:24:34,120
I think you should go to the hospital.

319
00:24:34,120 --> 00:24:38,680
You mean my problem is getting serious now?

320
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:42,760
I thought my blood pressure may be a little high since I can't sleep well at night.

321
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:45,060
The dizziness may be caused by high blood pressure.

322
00:24:45,060 --> 00:24:47,529
But it could also be an insufficient blood supply

323
00:24:47,529 --> 00:24:48,700
because your spine has been compressing your nerves.

324
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:51,139
So you better go to the hospital to get an X-ray.

325
00:24:51,139 --> 00:24:53,100
This way you will feel more relieved.

326
00:24:54,460 --> 00:24:56,070
My grandma is like you.

327
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:58,780
She has weak legs but she always refuses to go to the hospital.

328
00:24:58,780 --> 00:25:01,430
She is afraid that the body check would find a bunch of diseases.

329
00:25:01,430 --> 00:25:04,100
I learned acupuncture mostly for her.

330
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:12,750
I see, she is blessed to have a good grandson like you.

331
00:25:12,750 --> 00:25:17,979
Auntie, I think you should tell He Dun about your dizziness.

332
00:25:21,430 --> 00:25:23,470
You don't know much about her.

333
00:25:23,470 --> 00:25:27,790
Dun Dun has too many things on her shoulders.

334
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:30,880
She is quite depressed deep down.

335
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:35,800
I don't want her to worry about my health, too.

336
00:25:38,280 --> 00:25:40,280
Don't tell her.

337
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:43,629
I will go to the hospital for an examination, I will.

338
00:25:45,040 --> 00:25:46,780
I am back.

339
00:25:48,580 --> 00:25:51,260
Why did you two stop talking the moment I came back?

340
00:25:51,260 --> 00:25:53,830
You were talking about me behind my back?

341
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:55,470
I wouldn't dare.

342
00:25:55,470 --> 00:25:59,350
I was asking your mom what I could do to impress you.

343
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:05,110
Dun Dun, Xaio Ye is really a good young man.

344
00:26:05,110 --> 00:26:08,360
But mom will not intervene in young people's romantic relationships.

345
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:10,429
Jiahui just likes to joke.

346
00:26:10,429 --> 00:26:12,710
I'll go rinse some fruit for you.

347
00:26:14,800 --> 00:26:16,560
Thank you.

348
00:26:16,560 --> 00:26:19,020
I know you have your own reasons to do or not to do something.

349
00:26:19,020 --> 00:26:20,830
But sickness is not a trivial matter.

350
00:26:20,830 --> 00:26:23,280
You can't take it lightly.

351
00:26:23,280 --> 00:26:27,810
If you have any other questions, you can call me anytime.

352
00:26:27,810 --> 00:26:29,570
Okay.

353
00:26:29,570 --> 00:26:34,379
But I shouldn't trouble you or my daughter since you're busy at work all the time.

354
00:26:34,379 --> 00:26:37,169
You don't know how He Dun and I met, right?

355
00:26:37,169 --> 00:26:38,780
No.

356
00:26:38,780 --> 00:26:41,280
She saved my life.

357
00:26:49,450 --> 00:26:51,200
Really?

358
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:54,470
So you once had mental problems, too?

359
00:26:54,470 --> 00:26:56,960
It is said that it is difficult for a healer to heal himself.

360
00:26:58,400 --> 00:27:01,430
I just acted on impulse.

361
00:27:01,430 --> 00:27:03,230
You will be fine.

362
00:27:03,230 --> 00:27:06,069
I guess you two can help and support each other.

363
00:27:06,069 --> 00:27:08,880
You are both very decent young people.

364
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:12,560
And you both have this psychological shadow in your hearts which is haunting you.

365
00:27:12,560 --> 00:27:14,539
This is how interpersonal relationship works.

366
00:27:14,539 --> 00:27:16,829
People will support each other and move on.

367
00:27:16,829 --> 00:27:19,940
Dun Dun is a big girl now.

368
00:27:19,940 --> 00:27:22,430
But she is always alone.

369
00:27:22,430 --> 00:27:28,350
I hope she can be happy so that I can rest assured. You know what I mean?

370
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:30,400
Auntie.

371
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:34,610
Did something happen to He Dun before?

372
00:27:36,470 --> 00:27:38,730
No, no.

373
00:27:38,730 --> 00:27:42,530
It's all history.

374
00:27:42,530 --> 00:27:44,550
Let's not mention it.

375
00:27:50,230 --> 00:27:53,000
Dun Dun!

376
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:54,800
Dun Dun!

377
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:56,749
Dun Dun!

378
00:28:09,730 --> 00:28:11,570
Jiahui.

379
00:28:11,570 --> 00:28:12,849
Thanks a lot.

380
00:28:12,849 --> 00:28:14,370
How is she?

381
00:28:14,370 --> 00:28:17,379
She is asleep, have a seat.

382
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,520
Can I offer you something to drink?

383
00:28:21,520 --> 00:28:23,430
Coke then.

384
00:28:23,430 --> 00:28:25,710
We don't have coke.

385
00:28:25,710 --> 00:28:28,339
No one likes to drink that in my family, I'll go downstairs and buy you some.

386
00:28:28,339 --> 00:28:31,130
Forget it then. It's too much trouble, water is fine.

387
00:28:31,130 --> 00:28:32,560
Your mom can wake up at any time.

388
00:28:32,560 --> 00:28:35,210
I'm really sorry. I will remember it next time.

389
00:28:35,210 --> 00:28:36,750
Hold on.

390
00:28:40,930 --> 00:28:43,800
You must be a good amateur singer before.

391
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:47,050
That was when I was a kid.

392
00:28:47,050 --> 00:28:49,259
- I haven't sung for a long time.
- Thanks.

393
00:28:49,259 --> 00:28:51,480
You're welcome.

394
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:56,409
By the way, your mom's sickness should be caused by overthinking plus over-fatigue.

395
00:28:56,409 --> 00:28:59,680
I'll give her a few more acupunctures. That should do the trick.

396
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:01,099
Sorry to trouble you.

397
00:29:01,099 --> 00:29:04,409
No trouble at all. You saved my life.

398
00:29:07,210 --> 00:29:10,780
Actually, we should understand why senior people are always afraid of going to the hospital.

399
00:29:10,780 --> 00:29:14,379
They are just afraid that the result will show a lot of physical problems.

400
00:29:14,379 --> 00:29:16,309
My grandma is like this, too.

401
00:29:16,309 --> 00:29:19,549
Over time seeing a doctor will really become a taboo for them.

402
00:29:21,190 --> 00:29:22,920
Jiahui.

403
00:29:25,110 --> 00:29:28,070
I actually want to apologize to you

404
00:29:29,230 --> 00:29:31,900
because I've been suspicious of you.

405
00:29:31,900 --> 00:29:36,299
The way you showed up in front of me was too dramatic.

406
00:29:36,299 --> 00:29:41,450
And I always think you are a person with a lot of secrets.

407
00:29:48,980 --> 00:29:51,060
Many people still have little knowledge of mental health.

408
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:55,229
Some might refuse to talk or look at it, so many people will ignore their psychological problems.

409
00:29:55,229 --> 00:29:58,679
Over time the psychological problems will become physiological.

410
00:29:58,679 --> 00:30:02,630
Only when they realize something goes wrong with their bodies

411
00:30:02,630 --> 00:30:05,160
will they go to the doctor to check and verify.

412
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:07,589
And many patients can't get...

413
00:30:07,589 --> 00:30:10,690
the physical disease cured from ordinary medical treatment. This…

414
00:30:13,760 --> 00:30:17,929
Actually our psychological counseling office received a lot of intractable…

415
00:30:20,070 --> 00:30:22,500
In fact, they are caused by…

416
00:30:36,270 --> 00:30:40,410
[What are you doing now?]

417
00:31:09,070 --> 00:31:11,080
I knew I can find you in Director Fei's office.

418
00:31:11,080 --> 00:31:13,879
Why couldn't you knock when you came in, Sister?

419
00:31:13,879 --> 00:31:18,140
What? I need to ask for approval to chat with you in Director Fei's office.

420
00:31:18,140 --> 00:31:19,579
You know I've been busy recently.

421
00:31:19,579 --> 00:31:21,679
The show's audience rate has improved a bit recently.

422
00:31:21,679 --> 00:31:23,080
We've got to steady it.

423
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:25,909
Good for you, you've grown up.

424
00:31:25,909 --> 00:31:27,870
Then I will give you some reward.

425
00:31:28,520 --> 00:31:29,729
What reward?

426
00:31:29,729 --> 00:31:32,730
- The poster's budget has been approved.
- Really?

427
00:31:34,830 --> 00:31:36,680
The shooting is the day after tomorrow.

428
00:31:39,190 --> 00:31:42,900
Sister, you are like a real sister to me!

429
00:31:42,900 --> 00:31:46,379
My little fairy. My living bodhisattva!

430
00:31:46,379 --> 00:31:50,760
Tell Director Pan for me that I will fulfill this task perfectly.

431
00:31:50,760 --> 00:31:51,960
[Director's Office]

432
00:31:57,110 --> 00:31:58,820
[Qian Kaiyi]

433
00:31:58,820 --> 00:32:00,270
Excuse me.

434
00:32:06,590 --> 00:32:07,930
[Qian Kaiyi]

435
00:32:09,470 --> 00:32:12,359
It's okay. Just take it, It might be something important.

436
00:32:12,359 --> 00:32:14,089
He has nothing important to discuss with me.

437
00:32:14,089 --> 00:32:17,570
Hello, the subscriber you are calling is busy now…

438
00:32:18,870 --> 00:32:22,129
Hello, the subscriber you are calling is busy now…

439
00:32:22,129 --> 00:32:24,660
Oh my god.

440
00:32:24,660 --> 00:32:27,940
- Kaiyi, there's an emergency.
- What's wrong, Sister?

441
00:32:27,940 --> 00:32:29,900
Our photographer stood us up, He is going to a fashion week.

442
00:32:29,900 --> 00:32:32,249
- His schedule is available this afternoon only.
- This afternoon?

443
00:32:32,249 --> 00:32:34,950
Yes. It took me a lot of effort to book him for you this afternoon.

444
00:32:34,950 --> 00:32:37,210
This is so sudden! I haven't prepared anything.

445
00:32:37,210 --> 00:32:39,470
But if you want to wait, it'll be in another two weeks.

446
00:32:39,470 --> 00:32:41,730
if that's the case, I don't know the publicity period

447
00:32:41,730 --> 00:32:43,879
Director Pan arranged for us will…

448
00:32:43,879 --> 00:32:45,990
This afternoon it is!

449
00:32:46,940 --> 00:32:49,230
I'll contact He Dun now.

450
00:32:49,230 --> 00:32:51,729
Anyway, there is a show at night, so she has to come here anyway.

451
00:32:51,729 --> 00:32:54,230
So you haven't even contacted her yet?

452
00:32:54,230 --> 00:32:56,069
I've been trying to contact her.

453
00:32:56,069 --> 00:32:58,579
I kindly remind you that the photographer has a bad temper.

454
00:32:58,579 --> 00:33:00,069
And he's charged by the hour.

455
00:33:00,069 --> 00:33:03,929
So if anything goes wrong, the loss is from our own pocket.

456
00:33:05,740 --> 00:33:08,250
- I'll get prepared, Sister.
- Secure He Dun's presence!

457
00:33:08,250 --> 00:33:09,900
Consider it done!

458
00:33:11,130 --> 00:33:12,580
All right, I'll believe you can do it.

459
00:33:12,580 --> 00:33:16,029
I will have the time to play the Marvelous Snail.

460
00:33:17,930 --> 00:33:21,770
You just said you think I have a lot of secrets.

461
00:33:21,770 --> 00:33:23,950
Well, I stand corrected.

462
00:33:23,950 --> 00:33:26,330
I think everyone has many secrets.

463
00:33:26,330 --> 00:33:30,520
But I can't doubt you or deny you because of the secrets you have.

464
00:33:30,520 --> 00:33:32,960
And we have spent some time getting to know each other.

465
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:35,779
I don't think you are really that indifferent like you might look.

466
00:33:35,779 --> 00:33:37,470
You guys haven't had dinner yet, right?

467
00:33:37,470 --> 00:33:39,469
- I will cook for you.
- You can cook?

468
00:33:39,469 --> 00:33:42,140
I'm curious how you two met each other.

469
00:33:43,810 --> 00:33:46,199
I learned it when I was in school in northern China.

470
00:33:46,199 --> 00:33:48,430
I learned this to give my grandma treatment.

471
00:33:48,430 --> 00:33:51,459
- This is for me?
- It's called transcranial magnetic stimulator.

472
00:33:51,459 --> 00:33:53,779
Wear this helmet once a week for your physical therapy.

473
00:33:53,779 --> 00:33:56,399
Your hands will definitely get better.

474
00:33:56,399 --> 00:33:59,130
You seem to wrap and protect

475
00:33:59,130 --> 00:34:02,310
the softest part of your heart in a very hard shell.

476
00:34:04,620 --> 00:34:08,660
I mean, to some extent

477
00:34:08,660 --> 00:34:10,900
the two of us are alike.

478
00:34:17,160 --> 00:34:18,480
[Qian Kaiyi]

479
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:31,159
Mr. Qian, The studio is all set.

480
00:34:31,159 --> 00:34:32,869
We are ready when you are.

481
00:34:32,869 --> 00:34:35,319
- Let's get the shooting done ASAP.
- Sure.

482
00:34:35,319 --> 00:34:37,419
Give me another minute. No need to hurry.

483
00:34:37,419 --> 00:34:38,980
Help me explain, please?

484
00:34:38,980 --> 00:34:40,510
Okay.

485
00:34:59,200 --> 00:35:01,880
[Sorry, I accidentally annoyed you yesterday. I can try to explain to you if there's some misunderstanding. Are you available this afternoon?]

486
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:16,520
I'm sorry, We may not be able to shoot today.

487
00:35:17,359 --> 00:35:19,520
Our other host can't make it here on time.

488
00:35:19,520 --> 00:35:21,150
But don't worry, we will pay as we agreed.

489
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:22,910
This is our own mistake.

490
00:35:22,910 --> 00:35:25,710
- Can you explain to everyone for me?
- Sure.

491
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:27,960
- Sorry.
- It's all right.

492
00:35:55,130 --> 00:35:58,560
Lady, I'd need you to fill in this form.

493
00:35:58,560 --> 00:35:59,980
I don't need to fill the form.

494
00:35:59,980 --> 00:36:02,430
I just need to talk to Miss He.

495
00:36:02,430 --> 00:36:05,650
Here's the thing, Filling out the form will help visitor's to leave their information.

